ttps 的保护下，还要额外做签名验证？\r\n\r\n主要疑问，如 stripe 的退款接口\r\n```\r\ncurl https://api.stripe.com/v1/refunds -u \"$密钥:\" -d charge=$charge_id\r\n```\r\n\r\n就可以发起一笔订单的退款或者扣款。按照某些论述的话，没有签名的 Stripe 岂不是非常危险？", "content_rendered": "<p>注意场景：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>服务端对服务端的接口，不是客户端对服务端的接口</li>\n<li>防止中间人可以 PINNED Pub Key，因此中间人攻击不在考虑范围内</li>\n<li>极端条件可以使用客户端证书</li>\n</ul>\n<p>综合以上三点。为什么在 Https 的保护下，还要额外做签名验证？</p>\n<p>主要疑问，如 stripe 的退款接口</p>\n<pre><code>curl https://api.stripe.com/v1/refunds -u \"$密钥:\" -d charge=$charge_id\n</code></pre>\n<p>就可以发起一笔订单的退款或者扣款。按照某些论述的话，没有签名的 Stripe 岂不是非常危险？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1618228115, "replies": 93, "id": 770172}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_large.png?m=1615112453", "name": "linux", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_normal.png?m=1615112453", "title": "Linux", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux", "topics": 6117, "footer": "", "header": "Linux is a Unix-like computer operating system assembled under the model of free and open source software development and distribution.", "title_alternative": "Linux", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1615112453", "stars": 5498, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 11, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"username": "hushuguo", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5f213f6b432fa0875276aad46da66895?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hushuguo", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1617117375, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5f213f6b432fa0875276aad46da66895?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5f213f6b432fa0875276aad46da66895?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 540429}, "last_reply_by": "vinceying", "last_touched": 1618307662, "title": "终于有 Linux 官方的 QQ 了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/770249", "created": 1618277151, "content": "今天刚刚发现 qq 官网已经有了 linux 版本，快去下载呀 好兄弟们", "content_rendered": "今天刚刚发现 qq 官网已经有了 linux 版本，快去下载呀 好兄弟们", "last_modified": 1618277151, "replies": 61, "id": 770249}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1615111825", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1615111825", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 14510, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1615111825", "stars": 1776, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"username": "yitingbai", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a70fb36df294386f955107f7e0a7473a?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yitingbai", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1614580846, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a70fb36df294386f955107f7e0a7473a?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a70fb36df294386f955107f7e0a7473a?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 535331}, "last_reply_by": "lancelock", "last_touched": 1618254467, "title": "震惊! 宅男忍不住诱惑卖家诱惑, 怒拔黑苹果 Rx470 显卡!", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/770227", "created": 1618247267, "content": "我有一台黑苹果台式机, Rx470 4g 显卡,2 年前 350 元闲鱼买的,平时主力工作用. 听说显卡价格疯长就想拔下来卖了. 但是又因为工作用 , 一刻都不能耽误. 非常郁闷. \r\n\r\n\r\n...\r\n\r\n\r\n今天闲逛\\*鱼, 竟然有人在卖 Macbookpro 下半身, 性价比好高啊, 果断花了 2500 元买入一个. 到货后再卖掉显卡, 感觉赚疯了,哈哈哈...\r\n\r\n\r\n...\r\n\r\n\\*鱼上随便找了个卖家问价, 一听说我要卖卡, 就像打了鸡血一样, 话语间甚至让我产生了罪恶感, 感觉我耽误他挣钱了, 现在挖矿市场这么火爆吗? ??\r\n\r\n![6231618246895_.pic.jpg]( https://i.loli.net/2021/04/13/m5sj4ekipVaHBoS.jpg)\r\n\r\n![6241618246914_.pic.jpg]( https://i.loli.net/2021/04/13/UZVrcSuWswxnDB9.jpg)\r\n\r\n![6211618246814_.pic.jpg]( https://i.loli.net/2021/04/13/6tn8FB4JaruvEPX.jpg)\r\n\r\n![6221618246844_.pic.jpg]( https://i.loli.net/2021/04/13/UwCxBrHvfT7nDkp.jpg)", "content_rendered": "<p>我有一台黑苹果台式机, Rx470 4g 显卡,2 年前 350 元闲鱼买的,平时主力工作用. 听说显卡价格疯长就想拔下来卖了. 但是又因为工作用 , 一刻都不能耽误. 非常郁闷. </p>\n<p>...</p>\n<p>今天闲逛*鱼, 竟然有人在卖 Macbookpro 下半身, 性价比好高啊, 果断花了 2500 元买入一个. 到货后再卖掉显卡, 感觉赚疯了,哈哈哈...</p>\n<p>...</p>\n<p>*鱼上随便找了个卖家问价, 一听说我要卖卡, 就像打了鸡血一样, 话语间甚至让我产生了罪恶感, 感觉我耽误他挣钱了, 现在挖矿市场这么火爆吗? ??</p>\n<p><img alt=\"6231618246895_.pic.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/13/m5sj4ekipVaHBoS.jpg\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"6241618246914_.pic.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/13/UZVrcSuWswxnDB9.jpg\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"6211618246814_.pic.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/13/6tn8FB4JaruvEPX.jpg\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"6221618246844_.pic.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/04/13/UwCxBrHvfT7nDkp.jpg\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1618247286, "replies": 53, "id": 770227}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1596015931", "name": "create", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_normal.png?m=1596015931", "title": "分享创造", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/create", "topics": 16072, "footer": "", "header": "欢迎你在这里发布自己的最新作品！", "title_alternative": "Create", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1596015931", "stars": 3895, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 17, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"username": "catchexception", "website": "https://lawrenceli.me", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0873fbad8597de73ac68ea4d416e24ef?s=24&d=retro", "bio": "分布式架构、Kubernetes、Spring Cloud", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/catchexception", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1577159889, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0873fbad8597de73ac68ea4d416e24ef?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0873fbad8597de73ac68ea4d416e24ef?s=24&d=retro", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 460980}, "last_reply_by": "shunia", "last_touched": 1618308525, "title": "写了一个基于 Spring Cloud 的 WebSocket 分布式集群的一致性哈希实现", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/770165", "created": 1618226702, "content": "众所周知，WebSocket 服务是有状态的。给这样的服务做集群时会略微麻烦一点，因为客户端需要每次被路由到相同的服务实例上，而传统的 HTTP 服务一般视为无状态应用，也就不需要这样麻烦了。\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/Lonor/websocket-cluster\r\n\r\n本项目的前端配了一个简单的 React 页面展示客户端连接状态，利用了 Docker 的 Java SDK 来实现服务实例的上下线，同时使用了 RabbitMQ 、Redis 和 Nacos 等常见技术栈。有兴趣的同学可以 star 一波。\r\n\r\n更多方案参考我的博文： https://lawrenceli.me/blog/websocket-cluster\r\n\r\n![Websocket-Cluster]( https://github.com/Lonor/websocket-cluster/blob/main/demo.gif?raw=true)", "content_rendered": "<p>众所周知，WebSocket 服务是有状态的。给这样的服务做集群时会略微麻烦一点，因为客户端需要每次被路由到相同的服务实例上，而传统的 HTTP 服务一般视为无状态应用，也就不需要这样麻烦了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Lonor/websocket-cluster\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/Lonor/websocket-cluster</a></p>\n<p>本项目的前端配了一个简单的 React 页面展示客户端连接状态，利用了 Docker 的 Java SDK 来实现服务实例的上下线，同时使用了 RabbitMQ 、Redis 和 Nacos 等常见技术栈。有兴趣的同学可以 star 一波。</p>\n<p>更多方案参考我的博文： <a href=\"https://lawrenceli.me/blog/websocket-cluster\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://lawrenceli.me/blog/websocket-cluster</a></p>\n<p><img alt=\"Websocket-Cluster\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://github.com/Lonor/websocket-cluster/blob/main/demo.gif?raw=true\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1618226702, "replies": 51, "id": 770165}]